About this item

  • 【All-IN-1 Powerful Function】 SEAL: One-Press to SEAL ONLY, Easy Operation. DRY or MOIST Mode - Touch a single button to vacuum and seal dry or moist food. PULSE - Control the vacuum pressure manually. CANISTER - For jars, canisters, wine preservation. CANCEL- Stop the current operation at any time. Digital Countdown - To know the process of the vacuum and seal. Error Display - Let you know the problem and solution when using.
  • 【Widened Heat Seal】The food sealer equipped with 5mm Widened Heat Sealing Line and 12mm Sealing Strip, this feature guaranteed you every sealing is perfect. The heating line is wider than the normal vacuum sealer(2mm) and the 12mm sealing strip help the 5mm widened heating line to concentrate the heat much better. Every bag will get a widened seal, which will be more safe for you to protect food. The vacuum sealer Meeting your needs for bulk food sealing and packing.
  • 【Digital Countdown Display】 When vacuum sealing bags, the Digital LED Screen will countdown to show how long the process will be completed. And there will be an error display if the machine has been used wrongly. You can correct the operation to get a perfect seal according to the troubleshooting. It provides a user-friendly experience for all users. Note: Please do not lock the lid when storage. Moreover, the digital display is embedded in the panel background. If the sealer unplugged, the lid shows perfect wood grain. Such an artistic design!
  • 【11.8" Built-in Cutter, Bag Storage, with Bag Rolls】 This vacuum machine is designed with a built-in Cutter, and a Storage Container for bag rolls Inside. Also, it included 2 bag rolls (8"x6.6'), 5pcs Pre-cut vacuum sealer bags, you do not need to buy the sealing bag additionally. Considerable baffle on the Portable Liquid Tray helps you place sealing bag correctly.
  • 【90kPa 120W Powerful Suction】The Anybear vacuum sealer boasts 120 watts of high power to achieve a rapid vacuum speed of 6-12 seconds. The upgraded copper core pump ensures corrosion resistance, heat resistance, and friction resistance, delivering a stable and security suction power of up to 90KPA. The Anybear vacuum sealer is ETL certified. We provide Trusted Safety Use for every of our customers.
  • 【5 Year Warranty and Satisfied Service】You will receive 1 x vacuum sealer machine, 2 x vacuum bag rolls (8"x6.6'), 5x Pre-cut Vacuum bags (7.8"x11.8"), bags and rolls are BPA free, safe for Sous Vide, 1 x Air suction hose(inside the machine), 1 x Power Cord, 1 x User manual, We offer a 5-year warranty and friendly 24-hour customer service.

How customer reviews and ratings work

Customer Reviews, including Product Star Ratings help customers to learn more about the product and decide whether it is the right product for them.

To calculate the overall star rating and percentage breakdown by star, we don’t use a simple average. Instead, our system considers things like how recent a review is and if the reviewer bought the item on Amazon. It also analyzed reviews to verify trustworthiness.

  • Feline Reviewer
    5.0 out of 5 stars Very well designed in some aspects, falls short in others
    Reviewed in Canada on September 7, 2024
    Amazon Vine Customer Review of Free Product( What's this? )
    This unit is very well designed in some important parts, but also falls short in other aspects. I'll list the pros and cons below:

    Pros:
    - Very compact for a unit that has an integrated bag roll holder
    - Bag roll cutter clamps onto the bag and does a straight cut every time
    - Clamp style vacuum sealing makes it easier to line up the bag end to avoid excess gaps
    - Very powerful vacuum, will nearly instantly vacuum out the bulk of the air

    Cons:
    - Doesn't do well with moist foods, their moist mode vacuums for ~20s somehow and will suck liquids into the vacuum chamber
    - Any liquid that gets into the sealing strip area will have the bag not seal, need to press seal again or remove and seal further up (instructions mention this)
    - No ability to stop the pre-programmed mode and immediately seal, have to cancel the vacuum and press seal separately
    - Taped on sealing strip looks out of place, needing a sticker from Anybear saying "Do not peel off"...
    - Foam sealing sponges have a shorter lifespan than silicone ones, will absorb any liquids spilled into the chamber
    - Not able to remove the vacuum chamber for cleaning, have to wipe clean within the unit

    Despite all my complaints, it's mainly just bashing on their Moist pre-programmed mode. You can still get very good seals for moist contents by using the pulse mode. You can control how much it vacuums and then immedately seal before the liquids get to the sealing strip or vacuum chamber.

    The main issue would be the sealing sponges as that's not durable at all, they come with 1 set of replacements but you'll most likely need to ask Anybear for more during your 5 year warranty period.

    I would recommend this to others if they want a compact vacuum sealer with an integrated bag holder.
